<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Soch — Free Ops Audit</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Instrument+Serif:ital@0;1&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --coral: #EA6A47;
    --coral-dark: #C9522F;
    --coral-light: #FDF0EB;
    --charcoal: #1E1E1E;
    --mid: #4A4A4A;
    --light: #F7F4F0;
    --cream: #FDFAF6;
    --border: #E8E2D9;
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    background: var(--cream);
    color: var(--charcoal);
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* NAV */
  nav {
    padding: 20px 48px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--cream);
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 100;
  }
  .logo {
    font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif;
    font-size: 22px;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    letter-spacing: -0.3px;
  }
  .logo span { color: var(--coral); }
  .nav-tag {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--mid);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  /* HERO */
  .hero {
    max-width: 1080px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 80px 48px 64px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 420px;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .campaign-label {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    background: var(--coral-light);
    border: 1px solid #F0C4B4;
    color: var(--coral-dark);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 6px 14px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }
  .campaign-label::before {
    content: '';
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--coral);
  }

  h1 {
    font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif;
    font-size: clamp(38px, 5vw, 58px);
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -1px;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  h1 em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--coral);
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--mid);
    max-width: 520px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .proof-strip {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
  }
  .proof-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 12px;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--mid);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .proof-item::before {
    content: '→';
    color: var(--coral);
    font-size: 13px;
    margin-top: 1px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* FORM CARD */
  .form-card {
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 40px 36px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
    position: sticky;
    top: 80px;
  }

  .form-card-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--coral);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .form-card h2 {
    font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif;
    font-size: 24px;
    line-height: 1.25;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .form-card p {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--mid);
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .field {
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    color: var(--mid);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  input, select, textarea {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 11px 14px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 2px;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    background: var(--cream);
    outline: none;
    transition: border-color 0.15s;
    appearance: none;
  }

  input:focus, select:focus, textarea:focus {
    border-color: var(--coral);
    background: white;
  }

  textarea { resize: none; height: 88px; }

  .submit-btn {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 14px;
    background: var(--coral);
    color: white;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 2px;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background 0.15s, transform 0.1s;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }
  .submit-btn:hover { background: var(--coral-dark); }
  .submit-btn:active { transform: scale(0.99); }

  .form-footer {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: #AAAAAA;
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 14px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* DIVIDER */
  .section-divider {
    max-width: 1080px;
    margin: 0 auto 0;
    padding: 0 48px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  /* WHAT HAPPENS SECTION */
  .what-section {
    max-width: 1080px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 64px 48px;
  }

  .section-eyebrow {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--coral);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .what-section h2 {
    font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif;
    font-size: 36px;
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    max-width: 600px;
  }

  .steps-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2px;
  }

  .step {
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 32px 28px;
  }

  .step-num {
    font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif;
    font-size: 40px;
    color: var(--coral);
    opacity: 0.3;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .step h3 {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .step p {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--mid);
    line-height: 1.65;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  /* PROOF SECTION */
  .proof-section {
    background: var(--charcoal);
    padding: 64px 0;
  }

  .proof-inner {
    max-width: 1080px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 48px;
  }

  .proof-section .section-eyebrow { color: var(--coral); margin-bottom: 20px; }

  .proof-section h2 {
    font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif;
    font-size: 32px;
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .proof-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 2px;
  }

  .proof-card {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    padding: 32px;
  }

  .proof-card .outcome {
    font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif;
    font-size: 22px;
    color: white;
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .proof-card .detail {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    line-height: 1.65;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .proof-card .tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--coral);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  /* ABOUT STRIP */
  .about-strip {
    max-width: 1080px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 64px 48px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: center;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .about-strip h2 {
    font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif;
    font-size: 32px;
    line-height: 1.2;
    letter-spacing: -0.3px;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .about-strip p {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--mid);
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .stat-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 2px;
  }

  .stat-box {
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 24px;
  }

  .stat-num {
    font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif;
    font-size: 40px;
    color: var(--coral);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--mid);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  /* FOOTER */
  footer {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 24px 48px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    max-width: 1080px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  footer .logo { font-size: 18px; }
  footer p { font-size: 12px; color: #AAAAAA; }

  /* SUCCESS STATE */
  .success-state {
    display: none;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 20px 0;
  }

  .success-state .check {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    background: var(--coral);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto 20px;
    font-size: 22px;
    color: white;
  }

  .success-state h3 {
    font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif;
    font-size: 22px;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .success-state p {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--mid);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .calendar-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 12px 28px;
    background: var(--charcoal);
    color: white;
    border-radius: 2px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  /* ANIMATIONS */
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  .hero-left > * {
    animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease forwards;
    opacity: 0;
  }
  .hero-left > *:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.05s; }
  .hero-left > *:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.15s; }
  .hero-left > *:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.25s; }
  .hero-left > *:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.35s; }

  /* RESPONSIVE */
  @media (max-width: 860px) {
    .hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 48px; padding: 48px 24px; }
    .form-card { position: static; }
    .steps-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .proof-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .about-strip { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; padding: 48px 24px; }
    nav { padding: 16px 24px; }
    .what-section, .proof-inner { padding: 48px 24px; }
    footer { padding: 24px; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; text-align: center; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <div class="logo">Soch<span>.</span></div>
  <span class="nav-tag">AI Workflow Automation</span>
</nav>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-left">
    <div class="campaign-label">Free 20-minute audit</div>
    <h1>Your ops are <em>behind.</em><br>Let's fix the right things first.</h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">Your tools don't talk to each other. Your team is doing manual work that should be automated. You know it — you just haven't had time to fix it. We'll tell you exactly what to fix first, and why.</p>
    <div class="proof-strip">
      <div class="proof-item">No pitch deck. No fluff. Just a useful 20-minute conversation.</div>
      <div class="proof-item">We look at your current stack and tell you the 2–3 highest-impact automations for your business.</div>
      <div class="proof-item">You walk away with a clear picture — whether we work together or not.</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="form-card" id="formCard">
    <div class="form-card-label">Book your free audit</div>
    <h2>Tell us about your setup</h2>
    <p>3 questions. Takes 60 seconds. Then pick a time that works.</p>

    <form id="auditForm">
      <div class="field">
        <label>Your name</label>
        <input type="text" placeholder="Alex Chen" required>
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <label>Company</label>
        <input type="text" placeholder="Acme Inc." required>
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <label>Biggest ops headache right now</label>
        <textarea placeholder="e.g. Our CRM and Notion aren't connected, so someone manually updates both every day..." required></textarea>
      </div>
      <button type="submit" class="submit-btn">Book My Free Audit →</button>
    </form>

    <div class="success-state" id="successState">
      <div class="check">✓</div>
      <h3>Got it — pick a time below</h3>
      <p>We've noted your setup. Choose a 20-minute slot and we'll come prepared with specific ideas for your stack.</p>
      <a href="https://calendly.com/riz-withsoch/audit" class="calendar-btn" target="_blank">Choose a Time →</a>
    </div>

    <p class="form-footer">No spam. No obligation. Just a useful conversation.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="section-divider"></div>

<section class="what-section">
  <p class="section-eyebrow">What happens on the call</p>
  <h2>A 20-minute call that actually moves the needle.</h2>
  <div class="steps-grid">
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">01</div>
      <h3>We look at your stack</h3>
      <p>Walk us through what tools you're using and how your team actually works day-to-day. No prep needed — we ask the right questions.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">02</div>
      <h3>We identify the friction</h3>
      <p>We'll pinpoint the 2–3 places where manual work is costing you the most time, and tell you what automating each one looks like in practice.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">03</div>
      <h3>You leave with a clear picture</h3>
      <p>Whether we work together or not, you'll know exactly what to fix first and roughly what it takes — in time, cost, and effort.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="proof-section">
  <div class="proof-inner">
    <p class="section-eyebrow">What clients have said</p>
    <h2>What founders actually get out of working with us.</h2>
    <div class="proof-grid">
      <div class="proof-card">
        <span class="tag">Replaced a planned hire</span>
        <div class="outcome">"We were about to bring on an ops coordinator. Soch automated the exact work we were hiring for in three weeks."</div>
        <div class="detail">Founder, B2B SaaS — Seed stage. Saved an estimated $55,000 in annual salary costs.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="proof-card">
        <span class="tag">Saved 12 hours/week</span>
        <div class="outcome">"My team was spending half a day every week pulling data from three places to build a report. That's gone now."</div>
        <div class="detail">Founder, Professional services — Pre-seed. Automated reporting pipeline connecting Airtable, Notion and Slack.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="about-strip">
  <div>
    <h2>Built by founders, for founders who are done doing things manually.</h2>
    <p>Soch is an AI workflow automation consultancy. We work with B2B startup founders between pre-seed and Series A. We build automations using n8n, the Anthropic API, and the tools you already use — no rip and replace, no six-month implementation. We ship fast, document everything, and hand it over properly.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="stat-grid">
    <div class="stat-box">
      <div class="stat-num">2–4</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Weeks to first working automation</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-box">
      <div class="stat-num">3–5</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Workflows in a typical Core engagement</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-box">
      <div class="stat-num">0</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Rip-and-replace. We use your existing stack.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-box">
      <div class="stat-num">100%</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Documented + handed over on completion</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<footer>
  <div class="logo">Soch<span>.</span></div>
  <p>withsoch.com · riz@withsoch.com</p>
</footer>

<script>
  document.getElementById('auditForm').addEventListener('submit', function(e) {
    e.preventDefault();
    document.getElementById('auditForm').style.display = 'none';
    document.getElementById('successState').style.display = 'block';
    // In GHL: replace this with GHL form submission + redirect to calendar step
  });
</script>

</body>
</html>
